{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "92809dc1-fd5f-46b0-b62a-07168fffa4de", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/92809dc1-fd5f-46b0-b62a-07168fffa4de@2.pkg/1772597674040/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597674933", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/92809dc1-fd5f-46b0-b62a-07168fffa4de@2.pkg/1772597674040/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597674933"}, "identifier": "92809dc1-fd5f-46b0-b62a-07168fffa4de", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>一审题干；二审设问；三审题肢。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>②③：依据教材知识，青少年的情绪越发细腻且反应强烈、波动大，具有半成熟半幼稚的矛盾性特点。晓雯“想看电影被妈妈拒绝，一直闷闷不乐；经妈妈同意后，她喜笑颜开”，体现情绪波动大。“一直闷闷不乐，久久沉浸在电影的绝密任务中”，体现体现出细腻性，②③符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>故本题选C。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（原创）晓雯想看最近上映的电影《孤星计划》，却被妈妈拒绝，一直闷闷不乐，长时间不能摆脱郁闷的情绪；经妈妈同意后，她喜笑颜开，看完电影她却久久沉浸在电影的绝密任务中。这体现了青春期的情绪特点是（&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.0000pt;\">①情绪反应强烈&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;②情绪细腻性 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:15.0000pt;\">③情绪波动大 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;④情绪开放性</p>\n", "title": "（原创）晓雯想看最近上映的电影《孤星计划》，却被妈妈拒绝，一直闷闷不乐，长时间不能摆脱郁闷的情绪；经妈妈同意后，她喜笑颜开，看完电影她却久久沉浸在电影的绝密任务中。这体现了青春期的情绪特点是（  ）①情绪反应强烈         ②情绪细腻性     ③情绪波动大           ④情绪开放性", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/92